title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: Join GTA+ for Benefits
content:
Join Grand Theft Auto Online's premium Membership program, delivering exclusive benefits and rewards to GTA+ Members each month, including GTA$500,000 and more. The following are included through February 5:

— The new Vapid Dominator GT (Muscle)
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Terrorbyte Client Jobs
— 40% off Arcade Properties and their Upgrades and Modifications
— And more

GTA+ automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
